Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <gatesizes> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT gatesizes (expression?, gatesize*)>
 <!ATTLIST gatesizes
      condition           CDATA     IMPLIED
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
